### サーバー生存確認（GET）
GET http://localhost:8080/health


### DeciScope v1 health
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/health


### 会議作成
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/meetings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "価格改定デモ会議",
  "source": "fixture_replay"
}


### fixture一覧
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/fixtures


### fixture replay start
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/meetings/{{meeting_id}}/replay/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fixture": "demo.jsonl"
}


### durable events
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/meetings/{{meeting_id}}/events?after_seq=0


### transcript segments
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/meetings/{{meeting_id}}/segments?after_seq=0


### markdown report
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/meetings/{{meeting_id}}/report
Accept: text/markdown


### 会員登録フォーム（GET）
GET http://localhost:8080/register-form


### 会員登録API（POST）
POST http://localhost:8080/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test-user",
  "email": "kokoko@example.com",
  "password": "pass123"
}


### ログイン
POST http://localhost:8080/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "pass123"
}
